product_product.name: Faces Canada Prime & Fix Bag
product_product.short_description: Prep, set, GO! A miraculous duo of the Ultime Pro Primerizer and Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer, is here to make sure that your makeup always stays put. A limited edition bag with Face Canada's professional makeup essentials for all those gorgeous, jaw-dropping looks.
product_product.description:
#BeautifulBeignsWithYou
Faces Canada Prime & Fix Bag
Prep, set, GO! A miraculous duo of the Ultime Pro Primerizer and Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer, is here to make sure that your makeup always stays put. A limited edition bag with Face Canada's professional makeup essentials for all those gorgeous, jaw-dropping looks. Keep it for yourself or use it as the perfect gifting option - this chic combo bag will always stay en vogue!
About Ultime Pro Primerizer- A bridge between your skin and makeup, the Ultime Pro Primerizer leaves the skin feeling smooth and makeup ready .In built moisturizer and Shea butter keep the skin hydrated and a smooth surface for foundation application.The goodness of Vitamin E works as an antioxidant and enhances skin repair/regeneration. Silicon based formulation along with Micro shimmers give that lit-from-within look.
About Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer- A refreshing, light weight makeup fixing spray increases the staying power of your makeup and bars makeup meltdowns. Formulated with Moringa, Chamomilla Matricaria flower extract, Caffeine & Hyaluronic acid, it keeps the skin hydrated and protects it from radicals and pollutants.Recommended for all skin types, slay all day with the Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer.
From the start till the end, we've got you covered. Start your makeup regime with the Ultime Pro Primerizer Primer + Moisturizer. A 2-in-1 primer with built-in moisturizer minimises the appearance of fine lines. The anti-oxidant properties of Vitamin E and shea butter leaves the skin's surface hydrated, smooth and makeup ready. Follow this up with your daily makeup regime and give your makeup final finishing touches with Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer. Formulated with Moringa, Chamomilla Matricaria flower extract, Caffeine & Hyaluronic acid, it hydrates skin and protects it from radicals and pollutants
product_product.meta_description: Buy Faces Canada Prime & Fix Bag at Purplle.com.Prep, set, GO! A miraculous duo of the Ultime Pro Primerizer and Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer, is here to make sure that your makeup always stays put. A limited edition bag with Face Canada's professional makeup essentials for all those gorgeous, jaw-dropping looks.
product_product.meta_keywords: Faces Canada Prime & Fix Bag
product_product.meta_title: Faces Canada Prime & Fix Bag
product_product.directions_of_use:
1. Take a small amount of Faces Canada Ultime Pro Primerizer Primer + Moisturizer onto your finger tips
2. Create several dots on your cheeks, chin, forehead and nose
3. Using your finger tips or a sponge, spread the primer evenly
4. Follow-up with the Faces Ultime Pro Second Skin Foundation, and kick start your daily makeup regime
5. After you have finished applying your makeup, hold the Faces Canada Ultime Pro Makeup Fixer at arm's length, and spray on all the makeup applied areas. Now, just allow it to dry naturally without rubbing it in.

There are two ways to apply your lipstick. 
1. Line your lips with a matching lip liner. Apply the lipstick directly by pressing the lipstick on your lips with a light even pressure. Press your lips together to even out the color.

Katha

Product Description

Dr. Vaidyaâs HerboBuild is a natural supplement that supports optimal muscle growth and performance. Made from purely natural ingredients, HerboBuild contains a blend of 3 Ayurvedic herbs with proven benefits for muscle function, oxygen uptake, endurance, strength, and energy levels. These herbs have proven benefits that support athletic performance and muscle gain through their positive effects on testosterone and human growth hormone levels.

With absolutely no synthetic or chemical ingredients, this natural supplement for bodybuilders and athletes will give you a much needed boost, without exposing you to the high risk of side effects from steroids. Ingredient/Product Benefits

Ashwagandha

Regarded as a revitalizing herb or rasayana in Ayurveda, ashwagandha is the most effective natural supplement for muscle growth. Safed Musli

Safed musli is notable for its positive influence on the production of human growth hormone (HGH). Increased production of HGH is known to enhance muscle growth and aid tissue repair. This means that in addition to faster muscle gains it also reduces exercise recovery time.

Shatavari

Shatavari is an effective herb to support muscle growth because of its high content steroidal saponins that support increased testosterone production. Amino acids like asparagine in shatavari also support protein synthesis, which is an important factor for muscle growth.

100% Natural

Application: Nail Art Beauty, Nail Salon, Nail SPA or Training etc.Step 1) Clean Nails then trim nail surface as normal manicure process. Step 2) Fully shake up the polish, it can make the polish color be balanced. (Important). Step 3) Apply a thin layer of base coat and cure under UV lamp for 2 minute or an LED light for 30-60 seconds. (Necessary).
Step 4) Apply first layer of color gel and cure ander UV lamp for 2 minutes or under LED lamp for 30-60 seconds; when dry, apply the 2nd layer and cure with UV lamp or LED lamp again. Step 5) Apply the top coat and cure under a UV lamp for 2 minute or under LED lamp for seconds.
Step 6) Clean tacky layer with cotton soaked with cleanser or alcohol. 
To Remove: Step 1) Soak off the nails into acrylic remover for about 5 minutes, Step 2) Rip down the whole piece of nail enamel gently on each nail. Gentle Reminder: 1. Avoid all skin contact. If redness or other signs of adverse reaction occur, discontinue use immediately. 
2. Keep tightly sealed. Keep out of sunlight. Keep out of reach of children.

product_product.short_description: So feather-light, it doesnât feel like makeup! Introducing Lakme Matte Revolution Lipsticks - a collection of gorgeous matte lipsticks that are designed to be long-wear and infused with goodness of raspberry seed oil known for its deeply nourishing and soothing properties.
product_product.description:
So feather-light, it doesnt feel like makeup! Introducing Lakme Matte Revolution Lipsticks - a collection of gorgeous matte lipsticks that are designed to be long-wear and infused with goodness of raspberry seed oil known for its deeply nourishing and soothing properties. The creamy light formula glides on without dragging. Simply run the bullet over your lips once for instant glam. The buttery formula softly hugs lips and sets in a comfortable finish. Be assured of an intense colour payoff with just one application! Dont worry about a drying effect as it is enriched with nourishing properties that keep lips soft and tender. This range of lipsticks lasts throughout the day without weighing down your pout. It comes in a sleek bullet form that you can pop into your party clutch while heading out. From plums to pinks and nudes to corals, the range is available in 20 delicious shades. Make a statement with mattified, pretty lips!

How to use-Step 1- Dot centre of the mouth with your super-matte lipstick.Step 2- Work from the centre to the outer corner of your lips.Step 3- Glide evenly from end to end for a flattering, ultra-matte pout.
Pro Tip: Define lips with a lip liner for a sharp, super-sexy pout.
Key pointers
              A collection of creamy matte lipsticks 
              Feels extremely lightweight on lips
              Creamy formula sets with a light matte finish
              Delivers intense colour payoff
              One-stroke application for quick and easy use
              Infused with raspberry seed oil known to nourish and soothe lips
              20 expressive shades for daily wear as well as special occasions
